ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
PrecisReappointment of DEBORAH ANN GRACE MORRISH of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and designation of DEBORAH ANN GRACE MORRISH to be Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board of Canada (Toronto Regional Office), effective September 1, 2015.
